    "content": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"></span></p><hr/><p><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接入邮件后，客户往这个邮件发送内容时，客服可以通过微上客平台进行处理回复互动。</span></font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">第</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,sans-serif;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">步：注册微上客云客服账号</span></h2><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span></p><hr/><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">在微上客客服注册页面，填写您的邮箱、密码等信息，注册微上客账号。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\"></span><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-2-3-1.png\"></span></p><h2><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\">第2步：绑定邮件</span></h2><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span></p><hr/><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1、登陆微上客，进入<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“管理员模式”</span>&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">渠道管理</span>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">添加消息渠道</span>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">点击邮件</span>logo<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，添加邮件渠道</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-2-3-2.png\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">、点击</span><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">“</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\"><font face=\"宋体\">确认</font></span><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">，进入绑定页面，输入邮件渠道名称，及邮箱地址相关信息后保存。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-2-3-3.png\"></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><h2><br/></h2><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;color:#333333;font-weight:normal\"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>"
}